            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce is starting to thicken, drain and rinse the<strong> chickpeas</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for a further 10-15 min or until the potatoes are cooked through – this is your <strong>spiced stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
